OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FAny
OL,6,Flingering rain soon clearing eastern
OL,7,Fcounties to leave a generally fine
OL,8,Fevening with some late sunny spells.
OL,9,FLargely dry overnight with clear
OL,10,Fperiods. Winds falling light allowing
OL,11,Fisolated fog patches and perhaps some
OL,12,Fgrass frost in prone rural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FProbably starting dry with
OL,15,Fsome sunshine. Clouding over through
OL,16,Fthe morning, with scattered heavy
OL,17,Fshowers possible by the afternoon,
OL,18,Fthough many places staying dry.
OL,19,FFeeling fresher despite lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
